  "text": "In contrast to these findings, [CITATION_1] could not find a modulation of radiosensitivity by the treatment of MCF-7 cells with the active tamoxifen metabolite 4-hydroxytamoxifen (4OH-TAM). [CITATION_2] observed an Table 3 In vitro studies on the interaction of estrogens and ionizing irradiation in breast cancer cell lines. enhancement of radiation-induced apoptosis in MCF-7 cells which had been treated for 24 h with tamoxifen or the pure steroidal antiestrogen ZM 182780. The clonogenic survival of cells treated with ZM 182780 prior to irradiation was significantly reduced in comparison with irradiated untreated controls.",
